# Confidence Classification

Each assumption is assigned a confidence level based on evidence availability.

| Confidence | Definition |
|---|---|
| **High** | Direct manufacturer specification or documented facility information |
| **Medium** | Public evidence combined with engineering estimation |
| **Low** | Conservative proxy due to unavailable information |

